The act of travelling around, by airline or 'jetliner' (aka 'jet'). 

It's generally understood that the term jet setting came to be from people who could afford to travel to different locations around the globe, for the sake of travel, vacationing, and fun. (versus a military operation). It required lots of money to do this, so it was typically the rich and famous doing the travelling. They, as a loose group, were the JetSet, or the Jet Setters.